 uana 501 exam\n   • ☐ HB check in with Reika re: Tapiwa oral exam\n3. Trav
 el grants\n   • Lisa was waiting for me\, must've missed my email\n4. MS d
 egrees\n   • dept-wide message to students\n5. 602 TAs: send the names to 
